00:17:38.965 --> 00:17:40.950
And back to low.

00:17:40.950 --> 00:17:41.450
Cool.

00:17:41.450 --> 00:17:44.210
So you saw the music move
through-- one, two, three,

00:17:44.210 --> 00:17:46.695
four-- six different
pieces there.

00:17:46.695 --> 00:17:49.180
But it sounded like the
