00:43:44.620 --> 00:43:45.950
RICHARD LUDLOW: It
used to be a thing.

00:43:45.950 --> 00:43:47.990
ANDY FORSBERG: Yeah, it
used to be a huge thing.

00:43:47.990 --> 00:43:49.700
RICHARD LUDLOW: For
commercials, it was a big thing.

00:43:49.700 --> 00:43:51.180
